import { makeStyles } from "@mui/styles";

const personalStyle = makeStyles({
    Box : {
        margin: "0",
        padding: "0",
        height: "600px",
        width: "750px",
        boxShadow: "5px 10px 20px #000",
        display: "flex",
        flexDirection: "column",
        justifyContent: "center",
        alignItems: "center",
        gap: "2rem",
        borderRadius: "30px",
        userSelect: "none",
        background: "#fff",
    },
})

export default personalStyle
